channel.title: Hosting {First time} *check-up*
channel.description:
Well after being almost completely done with my server I wanted to put it online. Lots of work done to it, and well, I think it's ready. I portforwarded, (completely I think), changed the right IP's to my server equals and GUI's and so on...but there is that one problem, that is quite a big one...my server will not connect. I do not get what people say when they are trying to help with portforwarding through *writing or typing it all to me*, so just wondering if someone could please help me on teamviewer and see what the problem is :confused: confused, very confused...
Just comment below if you are willing to help, please don't just use a random comment, seeing that the page was commented on gives me "HOPE!" and I don't want to spend my time looking at someone say..."I can't help, sorry".
